    public class MacroscopicLinkSegmentTypeImpl
extends Object
implements org.planit.utils.network.physical.macroscopic.MacroscopicLinkSegmentType
    Each macroscopic link segment is of a particular type reflecting segment specific properties. On top of the segment specific properties each segment can have user class specific properties as well.
